{"tid":2344141,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個提神/保持精力嘅方法","createTime":"2020-12-28T12:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T14:58:29.000Z","uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43352ee8c9270755d31950815467ec379d4e2936","tid":2344141,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"早兩年份工好撚chur，作息唔定時，除咗飲完咖啡同瞓醒嗰陣個人都係迷住咁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，轉左兩份工到今時今日都仲係好容易攰，飲咖啡都開始唔係好有效，請問大家有冇咩絕招可以介紹吓？"},{"pid":"e0cd49f7bc80fc9c9fd962a76fd2467b3616064d","tid":2344141,"uid":74927,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:06:09.000Z","msg":"一累就冷手打個熱飛機提晨"},{"pid":"0ae9547d029653eae43249180acf628e6ac4406a","tid":2344141,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"真係頂唔順，又夠錢休息兩三個月就等個市好返啲 quit<br />\n要開始正常作息、還返啲睡眠債同埋停飲咖啡<br />\n<br />\n飲啲令你提神嘅野本身會嚴重影響你作息，同埋會 drain energy<br />\nquit 完之後開始每日訓返十粒鐘，幾個星期後身體需要嘅睡眠時間會慢慢變返正常<br />\n<br />\nsource: 英國 NHS<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nhs.uk/live-well/sleep-and-tiredness/why-lack-of-sleep-is-bad-for-your-health/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Flive-well%2Fsleep-and-tiredness%2Fwhy-lack-of-sleep-is-bad-for-your-health%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=844acf6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nhs.uk/live-well/sleep-and-tiredness/why-lack-of-sleep-is-bad-for-your-health/</a>"},{"pid":"4ba62962862ba67686e02d8c69e1d466ba6f0710","tid":2344141,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ae9547d029653eae43249180acf628e6ac4406a","tid":2344141,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"真係頂唔順，又夠錢休息兩三個月就等個市好返啲 quit<br />\n要開始正常作息、還返啲睡眠債同埋停飲咖啡<br />\n<br />\n飲啲令你提神嘅野本身會嚴重影響你作息，同埋會 drain energy<br />\nquit 完之後開始每日訓返十粒鐘，幾個星期後身體需要嘅睡眠時間會慢慢變返正常<br />\n<br />\nsource: 英國 NHS<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nhs.uk/l